oai_dc:dc.dc:title: David Anderson
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Tennessee State University
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: David Anderson Was the Founder of the First Student Organizations for Young Men. Originally Named the Billy Hale Jr. Club (In Honor of the President's son). The Club Was Renamed the Anderson-Billy Hale Club following Anderson's Sudden Death Christmas Day, 1915.
